name: Florre and Jasmine
description:
Florre was regarded as a holy priest who has the ability to heal people. Her position was important to the empire’s politics and influenced people's faith.

Although Florre has important position. But she enjoy sneaking away to explore the city and seek for delicious food. she is obstinate and playful but mature at the same time.

Her flower is Jasmine. It is also a symbol of purity and divinity. Someone call Jasmine is a “gift from God”.
